long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Unofficial feature for WhatsApp™ Web

Guess you are running a business over WhatsApp Web and your customers ask you the same questions the whole time. Wouldn't it be nice to keep the answers saved and to reply easy and fast? Then this Chrome Extension is exactly what you are looking for.

1. Open the extension to add your answers
2. Have fun!

Do you need something more? Write me.
¿Necesitas algo más? Escríbeme.

https://docs.google.com/forms/d/18Pl6lJAgbTDFyzOhfQKrk0-uPLz2Q5VGB_IsI6bYIpY
https://github.com/erostefano/whatsappweb-reply_buttons

WhatsApp is a trademark of WhatsApp LLC. This extension offers an unofficial feature for WhatsApp™ Web and is not related in any way to WhatsApp LLC.
